description:
I love hot, built, fucking Italian men and tonight we've pulled one from the War Chest for you. Antonio is short, built like a brick shit house, and has the attitude to match his great body. He's a real looker this one.

I met Antonio at a strip club one night as he spent his money trying to convince a stripper to come home with him. When the bitch ditched him and went out the back door, I told him I knew how he could make all that money back. Antonio followed me home and the rest is AD history.
title: Antonio
